License Scope Explanation:

PERMITTED USES (No Additional Authorization Required):
1. Lawful Use - Use only for lawful purposes in compliance with all applicable laws
2. Content Creation - Use the software to create content (videos, images, etc.) and commercialize it
3. Personal/Internal Use - Modify the software for yourself or your team's internal use
4. Open Source Distribution - Distribute the software (including modified versions) under AGPL terms

SPECIAL REQUIREMENTS FOR SaaS/ONLINE SERVICES:
Under AGPL v3, providing online services (e.g., SaaS) based on this software requires open-sourcing server-side modifications.

If you want to:
- Provide SaaS services based on this software
- Do not want to open-source your modifications
- Need commercial licensing and legal support

Obtain a commercial license:
Contact: admin@useying.com

Why This Licensing Approach?
Our goals are:
- To enable individual creators and open-source communities to use freely
- To ensure SaaS service improvements contribute back to the community
- To provide a legal licensing path for enterprises needing closed-source commercialization

